These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, cricket, basketball
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
2. the person drinking coffee is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | coffee   | almond-milk    | tea    | iced-tea |
| Sport      | basketball | snowboarding | cricket | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, cola, juice
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pomegranate, banana, potato
1. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
3. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
4. the person drinking coffee is not the person eating pomegranate##6
5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee  | cola    | lemonade | juice    |
| Food       | potato | pomegranate | banana  | cherry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, cola, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, scientist, bartender
1. the person drinking mirinda is not the journalist##6
2. the lawyer is not the person drinking cola##6
3. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the lawyer is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the lawyer##1
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the journalist is on the far left or far right##3
8. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | lemonade  | juice  | cola |
| Job        | scientist | bartender | lawyer | journalist  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, bird, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, van, skateboard, tram
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the lizard##6
4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | lizard | bird | dog     | cat |
| Transport   | van     | skateboard    | scooter | tram    |

