.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, subway, skateboard, roller
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
4. the person drinking tea is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person driving the airplane is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | tea |
| Transport   | roller | airplane | subway     | skateboard   |

