.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, comedy, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, thai, american, british
1. the canadian is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is not the thai##6
3. the canadian is on the far right##1
4. the thai is somewhere to the right of the british##5
5. the person watching comedy movies is the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
8. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the british##5
9. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the british##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy    | sports  | animation   |
| Nationality   | american  | british | thai | canadian |

