.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, horror, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, disco, ambient
1. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan dubstep##3
2. the fan disco is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
3. the person watching musical movies is the fan hip-hop##1
4. the fan dubstep is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
5. the fan disco is on the far left##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan dubstep##1
7. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | action | martial-arts     | horror | musical |
| Music-Genre   | disco | dubstep | ambient      | hip-hop         |

