.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, nurse, chef, teacher
1. the analyst is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
3. the teacher is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the nurse##3
6. the analyst is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the teacher##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | coffee        | almond-milk      | hot-chocolate          |
| Job        | analyst | nurse | teacher | chef |

