.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, security-guard, nurse, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, jet-ski, car
1. the coach is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is not the chef##6
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the car is the nurse##1
7. the coach is not the person driving the car##6
8. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | coach  | nurse | chef    | security-guard |
| Transport   | taxi | car | jet-ski | train  |

