.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, mouse, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, baseball, skateboarding, cycling
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the owner of the hamster##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the owner of the frog##6
7. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | mouse | hamster        | horse  | frog     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | cycling | baseball | skateboarding |

