.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, collecting, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, blues, country
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
2. the fan metal is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the fan blues is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan country and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the fan metal is between the fan hip-hop and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | card-games    | skydiving | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | metal | country   | blues     |

