.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, kale, artichoke, kiwi
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, car, subway
1. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
2. the person eating kiwi is not the person driving the van##6
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person driving the car is not the person eating kiwi##6
6. the person eating kale is not the person driving the van##6
7. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
8. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | watermelon  | artichoke | kale | kiwi |
| Transport   | car | van     | subway     | quad-bike    |

