.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, eggplant, grapefruit, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, spy, action, mystery
1. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
2. the person eating eggplant is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person eating plum is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
5. the person eating plum is between the person eating eggplant and the person watching animation movies##2
6. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | zucchini | eggplant      | plum | grapefruit   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | action | mystery   | animation |

