.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, coffee, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, milksy, romance
1. the person watching milksy movies is not the person drinking 7up##6
2. the person watching milksy movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking iced-tea##2
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching milksy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | 7up       | iced-tea | milk     | coffee     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | milksy       | romance | zombie |

