3. the person who's sport is handball is not the accountant##6
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is between the coach and the person who's sport is handball##2
6. the coach is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
7. the fisherman is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | accountant  | musician | fisherman | coach |
| Sport   | soccer | handball | rugby   | biathlon |

