5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | sprite | almond-milk | lemonade         |
| Sport      | surfing | climbing | rowing          | sailing |

