.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, fishing, photography
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, rat, cat
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the cat is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | fishing | hiking | photography |
| Pet     | rat  | guinea-pig      | snake  | cat       |

