2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the trike is not the person drinking juice##6
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
6. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice | cola | coffee      | tea   |
| Transport   | scooter  | jet-ski   | subway | trike |

 